author: Marvel Entertainment
description:
🌊 Journey with MARVEL Mystic Mayhem in Version 1.2: Siege in the Deep — as Atlantis falls into shadow and Namor fights to reclaim his throne.

Torn from his crown by a monstrous usurper, Namor descends into exile — gathering strength, rallying heroes, and braving the abyss to reclaim what is his.

But in the heart of the deep, the truth surfaces: the throne is no prize of kings, but a mirror. The monster upon it… is Namor himself.

⚔️ Will Namor rise as ruler of the deep — or sink into the abyss he created?
